comment: Cauley-Stein (SAC) makes contact to the body of Griffin (LAC), affecting his shot attempt.

Cauley-Stein (SAC) turns into Paul (LAC) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
McLemore (SAC) clears the lane within three seconds.
Jordan (LAC) sets the screen on Tolliver (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Rivers (LAC) legally contests Hield's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
McLemore (SAC) legally contests Crawford's (LAC) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Griffin (LAC) obtains a legal guarding position and jumps vertically as he contests McLemore's (SAC) driving shot attempt.
Griffin (LAC) makes marginal contact with Cauley-Stein (SAC) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Galloway (SAC) makes incidental contact with Paul (LAC) that does not affect his FOM.
Jordan (LAC) sets the screen on Galloway (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Hield (SAC) legally contests Paul's (LAC) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
